import React from 'react';

const Logo = ({ className }) => {
  return (
    <svg
      className={className}
      width="132"
      height="40"
      viewBox="0 0 132 40"
      fill="none"
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      aria-hidden="true"
      focusable="false"
    >
      <defs>
        <linearGradient id="cn-grad" x1="0" y1="0" x2="1" y2="1">
          <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#7C3AED"/>
          <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#F472B6"/>
        </linearGradient>
        <filter id="soft-shadow" x="-20%" y="-20%" width="140%" height="140%">
          <feDropShadow dx="0" dy="3" stdDeviation="6" floodColor="#000" floodOpacity="0.2" />
        </filter>
      </defs>

      {/* Circular gradient badge */}
      <g filter="url(#soft-shadow)">
        <circle cx="20" cy="20" r="18" fill="url(#cn-grad)" />
      </g>

      {/* Paperclip icon */}
      <path
        d="M15 22.5L24 13.5C25.933 11.567 29.067 11.567 31 13.5C32.933 15.433 32.933 18.567 31 20.5L20.75 30.75C18.402 33.098 14.598 33.098 12.25 30.75C9.902 28.402 9.902 24.598 12.25 22.25L22 12.5"
        stroke="#0F0B1A"
        strokeWidth="2.2"
        strokeLinecap="round"
        strokeLinejoin="round"
      />

      {/* Wordmark 'Clipnest' - drawn as vector for crispness */}
      <g transform="translate(44,8)">
        <path fill="url(#cn-grad)" d="M0 12c0-6.627 5.373-12 12-12 2.06 0 3.99.49 5.69 1.36l-1.74 3.5C14.7 4.3 13.39 4 12 4 7.582 4 4 7.582 4 12s3.582 8 8 8c1.39 0 2.7-.3 3.95-.86l1.74 3.5C15.99 23.51 14.06 24 12 24 5.373 24 0 18.627 0 12z"/>
        <rect x="26" y="0" width="4" height="24" rx="2" fill="url(#cn-grad)"/>
        <path fill="url(#cn-grad)" d="M38 2h4v20h-4V2z"/>
        <path fill="url(#cn-grad)" d="M50 2h4v20h-4V2z"/>
        <path fill="url(#cn-grad)" d="M62 2h4v12.5c0 5.8 8 5.8 8 0V2h4v13c0 8.6-16 8.6-16 0V2z"/>
      </g>
    </svg>
  );
};

export default Logo;
